<div>
	Here is a great recipe:<br />
	<br />
	Take one part of Basil oil, two parts of Peppermint oil and one part of Lavender oil, put them into a dropper bottle and give it a good shake. When needed, just put a few drops onto a tissue and breathe in the aroma. If the headache is specifically muscle related, then it is best to add some of this blend to a carrier oil and use it as a wonderful, soothing neck massage.&nbsp;</div>
